# secureblue-iot-dnsserver

A work-in-progress project with the goal of providing a bootc image that works as out of the box DNS server with zero manual configuration required.

Features:
 - DNSSEC enabled
 - Pi-hole 
 - inbound DoT and DoH support
 - dnscrypt-proxy for upstream resolver connections
 - strict systemd sandboxing
 - strict SELinux confinement
